Bundled binaries (checked into this repository)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

android/app/src/main/assets/ggml-hexagon/libggml-htp-v*.so
  Qualcomm Hexagon (HTP/QNN) backend libraries for ggml/llama.cpp, shipped by
  llama.rn (node_modules/llama.rn/bin/arm64-v8a). They let llama.cpp offload to
  a Qualcomm Snapdragon NPU; on other SoCs (e.g. Google Tensor) they are unused
  and inference falls back to CPU. These are prebuilt binaries redistributed
  from the llama.rn package. See llama.rn and llama.cpp (MIT) below, and the
  Qualcomm AI Engine Direct (QNN) SDK license for the Hexagon components.

